Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:44.24,jp-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,世良
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:44.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Sera.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:45.00,jp-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ウィス
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:44.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
