Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:47.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Hiroi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.59,0:21:48.16,jp-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オッス
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:48.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.02,0:21:49.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Kiyogawa.
